I"I<div class="p">Run, partisan, run after me,</div>
<div class="p">See how delightfully I flee!</div>
<div class="p">On feet as wings beside the grass,</div>
<div class="p">While yours the tender hill impress.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Despite dark words upon your lips,</div>
<div class="p">From mine shall fly red cherry pips.</div>
<div class="p">The rot across your mien shall spread,</div>
<div class="p">As mine is blooming cherry red.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">We sprint, the two of us, along</div>
<div class="p">This pass, my lips around a song,</div>
<div class="p">Yours on a curse; my laughing face</div>
<div class="p">Leads your black scowl through the race.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Words float to reach my distant ear:</div>
<div class="p">The humming of a drone I hear,</div>
<div class="p">With every sound delightfully</div>
<div class="p">Immingled with the sound of glee.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Now wafts a 'Speak,' there 'Voting' flies,</div>
<div class="p">Here 'Action' sounds, there 'Duty' lies.</div>
<div class="p">Endeavor is too slight to snare</div>
<div class="p">These tones so heavy on the air.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Though solemnly I strain to hear</div>
<div class="p">The sounds you huckster at my ear,</div>
<div class="p">The day's too bright, the sun's too high</div>
<div class="p">To desolate a fine July.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Run on, my friend! I'll run before,</div>
<div class="p">With panting breath, our muscles sore,</div>
<div class="p">Our neighbors cheering from the town</div>
<div class="p">The two of us, both up and down.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">What fun! what fun! is ours fore'er:</div>
<div class="p">The sunlight streams upon our hair:</div>
<div class="p">As light rolls to the flowering earth,</div>
<div class="p">Our clamor flies to Heaven's berth.</div>
